<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=0, user-scalable=no'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" media="screen" title="no title" charset="utf-8">
    <title>Happy Company</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="main-container">
      <header class="header-logo">
        <img src="images/logo.png"/ alt="Happy Sweets">
      </header>
      <div class="header-container">
        <div class="header-text">
          <p>
            You can’t have luck without Happy Sweets!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="images/logo.png" alt="Happy Sweets" />
        </div>
        <div class="doodle">
          <img src="images/face.png" alt="face" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <main>
        <article>
          <h2>No more tears and anxiety,</br>just happiness and joy!</h2>
          <p>
            It’s soft-shelled, and jelly on the inside. Happy Sweets gives you an inebriety of euphoria and happiness. It has all the benefits of cocaine without the disadvantages. Enjoy a woolly bonanza with Happy Sweets! Euphoric, narcotic, pleasantly hallucinant…
          </p>
        </article>
      </main>
      <main class="prize">
        <article class="">
          <h3>A year's worth of Happy Sweets</h3>
          <form class="" action="index.html" method="post">
            <h4>Name:</h4><br>
            <input type="text"><br>
            <h4>E-mail:</h4><br>
            <input type="text"><br>
            <h4>Company name:</h4><br>
            <input type="text">
          </form>
        </article>
      </main>
      <footer>
        <p>
          © Happy Company
        </p>
        <p>
          All Rights Reserved
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
